@startuml
title BidMart Current Context Diagram
left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "Buyer/User" as Buyer <<User>>
actor "Seller/User" as Seller <<User>>
actor "Admin" as Admin <<User>>

component "BidMart Auth/Core Interfaces\nlogin, account settings,\nmarketplace use" as UserInterface <<Frontend>>
component "BidMart Admin Interface\nadministration and moderation" as AdminInterface <<Frontend>>
component "BidMart Platform" as Platform <<System>>
cloud "Email Provider\nverification, password reset, MFA email" as Email <<External System>>

Buyer --> UserInterface : uses BidMart
Seller --> UserInterface : uses BidMart
Admin --> AdminInterface : uses admin interface
UserInterface --> Platform : HTTPS
AdminInterface --> Platform : HTTPS
Platform --> Email : sends auth/security email

note bottom of Platform
Context diagram intentionally hides databases.
Database ownership is shown only in container
and deployment diagrams.
end note
@enduml
